9 REQUIREMENTS OF THE FEDERAL EMERGENCY MEDICAL TREATMENT AND ACTIVE
10 LABOR ACT;
11 (III) MEDICALLY NECESSARY SERVICES IF THE MANAGED CARE
12 ORGANIZATION AUTHORIZED, REFERRED, OR OTHERWISE ALLOWED THE ENROLLEE
