15 EMERGENCY FACILITY; AND
16 (IV) MEDICALLY NECESSARY SERVICES THAT RELATE TO THE
17 CONDITION PRESENTED AND THAT ARE PROVIDED BY THE PROVIDER IN THE
18 EMERGENCY FACILITY TO THE ENROLLEE IF THE MANAGED CARE ORGANIZATION
